title: I was 16/2 and lost game
body:
I was playing leblanc and I was 16/2 because I won my lane and ganked other lanes and killed the enemy jungler when he ganked me.
Had tp and ganked bot and top.

But Jungler fed, Bot fed, top fed.
I was the only one with kills basically except for  the times my teammates ks'd me.

Lost game because i can't 1 vs 5. Team cant defend tower against the caitlyn the kept feeding.
Everytime I shut her down i almost die because of how fed she got.
Eventually she got fed and could 1 shot me and we lost game.
